than just a mobile wallet.

00:04:01.700 --> 00:04:03.440
And what you will
hear from us today,

00:04:03.440 --> 00:04:08.390
is our efforts at really
making this happen.

00:04:08.390 --> 00:04:10.990
So we want Android Pay
therefore to be everywhere

00:04:10.990 --> 00:04:13.054
