spend a lot of
time on mobile web.

00:15:39.080 --> 00:15:44.280
The time spent is skews
more towards mobile apps.

00:15:44.280 --> 00:15:45.900
The fact of the
matter is, something

00:15:45.900 --> 00:15:52.130
like half of all transactions
happen on mobile web.

00:15:52.130 --> 00:15:56.120
But mobile web does not
have any of the support

00:15:56.120 --> 00:15:57.390
that in-apps have had.

00:15:57.390 --> 00:16:00.790
It's a different
programming model.

00:16:00.790 --> 00:16:02.560
And the result is
that you and I are

00:16:02.560 --> 00:16:05.679
stuck with really long payment
forms, and it's really long,

00:16:05.679 --> 00:16:07.720
you know, details forms,
that we have to fill out

00:16:07.720 --> 00:16:09.511
very slowly on tiny keyboards.

00:16:09.511 --> 00:16:10.760
And it doesn't work that well.

00:16:10.760 --> 00:16:11.890
We give up pretty often.

00:16:11.890 --> 00:16:15.580
Conversion rates are pretty low.

00:16:15.580 --> 00:16:20.360
So we took a baby step last year
and were stunned by the results

00:16:20.360 --> 00:16:22.100
that we saw.

00:16:22.100 --> 00:16:27.450
