your Google payment credentials

00:16:32.260 --> 00:16:34.760
that you put into Android Pay,
that you have put into Google

00:16:34.760 --> 00:16:39.200
Play, and have it be
available for form fill-out

00:16:39.200 --> 00:16:42.000
on mobile web.

00:16:42.000 --> 00:16:47.660
Again, for users that actually
used Payment Autofill,

00:16:47.660 --> 00:16:50.620
you know for check
out, the merchants

00:16:50.620 --> 00:16:54.260
saw a 25% increase
in conversion rate.

00:16:54.260 --> 00:16:56.864
Again, a staggering
number where wins

00:16:56.864 --> 00:17:02.680
come in half, and quarter,
and single digit percentages.

